{"tid":1548073,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"（我願榮光歸香港）唱到既英文歌詞","createTime":"2019-09-07T01:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:57:59.000Z","uid":99268,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e759042b2e38cb5ae5df1623ac5856f774f6d3c1","tid":1548073,"uid":99268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:58:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=4ab66fa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n老實講，片入面的英文歌詞真吾係好唱得，所以自己做左一個比較流利D既翻譯：<br />\n<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\nTo the Glory of Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\nWhy should our tears fall on the land?<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\nWhy should anger run in our band?<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\nArise, once again, let our voice ring out:<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\nLiberty will come about!<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\nWhen fear makes its stain on our land,<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\nWhen truth calls to us, come out and stand!<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\nWhen blood flows throughout, yet still our voices stay and shout,<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n&ldquo;Free and glo-rious Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n在晚星 墜落 徬徨午夜<br />\nLet the stars be dark, let night be long,<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處吹來 號 角 聲<br />\nFrom the mist emerges now our Bat-tle Song:<br />\n&quot;捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n&ldquo;Soldier On! Let all come as one, let all fight as one;<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也永不滅&quot;<br />\nOur soul and spirit never fade!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\nBring on the dawn: Liberate our Hong Kong!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\nComrade of mine: Revolution of Our Time!<br />\n祈求民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\nTo freedom and lib-er-ty; forever we fight for thee!<br />\n我願榮 光歸香港<br />\nTo the glor-y of Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"6224d8614d8436f14cda5f5383a84e1f229dde03","tid":1548073,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4054c29fec1fbb8bdc680efe65f2ef4416caeec","tid":1548073,"uid":299255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:03:08.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb77606e2d1d3ef427240705f1bfe950d8b84b4","tid":1548073,"uid":122001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0b74cbed25267e335f926733c03590de7d727b","tid":1548073,"uid":122001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"不過都係心屬粵語版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080d1eba04daabc1368560ca9b91ebd378a7ec13","tid":1548073,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5334435fb42f34a1a4bc8a66e9ef17dc96a1a16","tid":1548073,"uid":46299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:19:44.000Z","msg":"喺心入面唱都起晒雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1b6f784069ff2888a13f65ae5f35c62bbf7e42","tid":1548073,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"828cbdeea11247f6b1be8401e586a3bedd01359b","tid":1548073,"uid":298061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"推唔郁<br />\n填得好好<img src=\"/asse